==English==

===Etymology===
From {{etyl|fr|en}} {{term|acerbité|lang=fr}}, from {{etyl|la|en}} {{m|la|acerbitās||acerbity; harshness}}, from {{term|acerbus||bitter|lang=la}}. See [[acerb]].

===Pronunciation===
* {{a|UK}} {{IPA|/əˈsɜːbɪti/|lang=en}}
* {{audio|en-uk-acerbity.ogg|Audio (UK)|lang=en}}
* {{a|US}} {{IPA|/əˈsɝbɪdi/|lang=en}}
* {{audio|en-us-acerbity.ogg|Audio (US)|lang=en}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun|acerbities}}

